text: "Peaches" is a 1977 song by English rock band The Stranglers and is the second single from their debut studio album Rattus Norvegicus. It went to number 8 in the United Kingdom. It was banned by the BBC for using coarse sexual language and innuendo in the lyrics. == References == Category:1977 songs Category:The Stranglers songs Category:Punk rock songs
title: Peaches (The Stranglers song)
